<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.2.4">
<l>ciṟiyā yōrpiḷḷaiyumā  yulakuṇṭō rālilaimēl</l>
<l>uṟaivā yeṉneñciṉuḷ ḷēyuṟaivā yuṟaintatutāṉ</l>
<l>aṟiyā tiruntaṟiyē ṉaṭiyēṉa ṇivaṇṭukiṇṭum</l>
<l>naṟaivā rumpoḻilcūḻ naṟaiyūrniṉ ṟanampīyō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who dwells, as a tiny babe, on a banyan leaf having eaten the earth,</l>
<l>You dwell inside my heart; I, [your] servant,</l>
<l rend="indent">do not [ever] know of not knowing</l>
<l>That [you] dwell [there], O noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr</l>
<l>Encircled by groves where drips honey and where beautiful bees burrow.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
